Relics Of Humanity - Ominously Reigning Upon The Intangible (2014)


The darkest emperor is enthroned, he beholds as obscurity gorging millions of fallen souls and transforming them into the void.
All that is holy is on fire... ...This album consists of harmony, dark technical and low as fuck slamming parts.
No plastic sounds, no drum machines, no other modern shits.
True ungodly brutality for true brutalheads !!



Influences:

Disgorge (USA), Suffocation, Immolation, Deprecated, Obscured Secretions, Decrepit Birth .....
